---

This project is a companion toolkit for, and depends on, the upstream project:

  vercel-labs/agent-browser  (Apache-2.0 / MIT, see https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-browser)

silent-browser-use does NOT redistribute agent-browser source. It invokes the
upstream `agent-browser` binary as a subprocess. All browser-automation
credit belongs to the agent-browser maintainers.

This project also draws design inspiration (persistent agent window pattern)
from:

  browser-use/browser-harness  (https://github.com/browser-use/browser-harness)

Both upstream projects retain their respective licenses; nothing here
relicenses upstream code.
